cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.CY 

This paper deals with text-mining and topic modelling in software repositories, which falls under the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Cybersecurity (cs.CY). However, since the focus is on text analysis and topic modelling, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories.
